description:
&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity to join our busy Admin Team working as a Senior Administrator within Peterborough Adult Locality Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work closely &lt;span&gt;with Admin Lead&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;clinical managers. You will&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;provide senior administrative support and assist with recruitment, procurement, health roster, line management of administrators and take operational responsibility for them, allocation of work and deputise in the absence of the Admin Team Lead. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a busy role and requires the post holder to be flexible and adaptable, work well under pressure and have good team management skills. You will be a proactive person with strong administrative skills including IT and communication skills. Previous experience of line management is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is 30hrs/week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anna Palutek - Admin Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;anna.palutek@cpft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01733 748484&lt;/p&gt;
